{"TopicId":185819,"ForumId":66,"TopicTitle":"KSP Loading... Preview: Grip Pads","CreatedByName":"St4rdust","CreatedById":196576,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-06-25T14:55:26Z","PageNum":2,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Guest","CreatedById":-1,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-06-26T05:15:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYES!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis just keeps getting better and better. It looks like Breaking Ground didn\u0027t just unleash some mad\u00A0kerbal energy among us players...!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n(Now how about wheels we could mount on rotors? Pretty please...?)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-06-26T06:07:10Z\u0022 title=\u002206/26/2019 06:07  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00225 yr\u0022\u003EJune 26, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by Guest\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"RealKerbal3x","CreatedById":183830,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-06-26T05:28:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis is very cool. Walker time!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Starwaster","CreatedById":71262,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-06-26T06:01:23Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223625368\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022185819\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221561526898\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022183830\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022RealKerbal3x\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n32 minutes ago, RealKerbal3x said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis is very cool. Walker time!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nUh? What do zombies have to do with Kerbal Space Program?\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:confused:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 data-ratio=\u0022105.88\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_huh.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:confused:\u0022 width=\u002217\u0022\u003E\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:confused:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 data-ratio=\u0022105.88\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_huh.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:confused:\u0022 width=\u002217\u0022\u003E\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:confused:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 data-ratio=\u0022105.88\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_huh.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:confused:\u0022 width=\u002217\u0022\u003E\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:confused:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 data-ratio=\u0022105.88\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_huh.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:confused:\u0022 width=\u002217\u0022\u003E\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:confused:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 data-ratio=\u0022105.88\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_huh.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:confused:\u0022 width=\u002217\u0022\u003E\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:confused:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 data-ratio=\u0022105.88\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_huh.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:confused:\u0022 width=\u002217\u0022\u003E\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:confused:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 data-ratio=\u0022105.88\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_huh.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:confused:\u0022 width=\u002217\u0022\u003E\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:confused:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 data-ratio=\u0022105.88\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_huh.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:confused:\u0022 width=\u002217\u0022\u0